newIframeWindow(doc : HTMLDocument, width : Int, height : Int) : HTMLIFrameElement

Creates a new iframe intended to be used as a window. This iframe will not have borders, will not allow resizing, will not have any margin or padding, and will be transparent (depending on the body).
